videos.description: Cody Martin gets the steal then makes a nice bounce pass to Lindsey Drew in transition for the and-1 bucket.
videos.headline: Nevada's tough defense leads to offense

videos.description: Entering the game at 0-4 as a ranked team this season, Nevada cruises to an 83-58 win over San Diego State.
videos.headline: Nevada picks up first win as ranked team
